Package: mediaconch
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Implementation checker, policy checker, reporter, and fixer
 that targets preservation-level audiovisual files (specifically Matroska,
 Linear Pulse Code Modulation (LPCM) and FF Video Codec 1 (FFV1)).
 .
 This project is maintained by MediaArea and funded by PREFORMA.
 .
 This package includes the command line interface.

